Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.45,0:35:24.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,重点在于 我一直热爱\N{\fs90}The point is, I have always loved
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.65,0:35:26.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙滩车的灵魂\N{\fs90}the spirit of the beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.32,0:35:28.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,我热爱创造它的时代还有那个时代的一切\N{\fs90}I love the era that created it and all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.99,0:35:31.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是有一件事我不喜欢\N{\fs90}But the one thing that's made me not like it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.39,0:35:33.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,这引擎让我想起希特勒\N{\fs90}is the engine reminds me of Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.93,0:35:38.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经杀掉我体内所有希特勒的DNA了\N{\fs90}I have removed all of that Hitler DNA from mine,
