Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.20,0:35:42.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,它走火入魔了\N{\fs90}It's gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.50,0:35:45.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这是弗兰肯斯坦的车  -我来终结争论\N{\fs90}- It's Frankenstein's buggy. - I can settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.54,0:35:47.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你的车不算是合格的沙滩车  -不算\N{\fs90}- Yours isn't a proper beach buggy. - It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.94,0:35:50.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,-但相比你更算是沙滩车  -扯淡\N{\fs90}- But it's more of a beach buggy than yours. - Oh, rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.81,0:35:53.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为沙滩车真正的灵魂\N{\fs90}Because the true spirit of the beach buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.45,0:35:55.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是甲壳虫的地板和引擎 他的车有\N{\fs90}is the Beetle floorpan and engine, which his has.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.45,0:35:56.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的车引擎都不过关\N{\fs90}Yours doesn't have the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.55,0:35:57.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我的车啥都有\N{\fs90}Mine actually has everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.65,0:35:59.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车才是合格的沙滩车\N{\fs90}Mine is the proper beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.45,0:36:01.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,-抱歉 但是...  -你才不抱歉\N{\fs90}- I'm sorry about this, James, but... - You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.52,0:36:03.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的车是放纵的60后造的\N{\fs90}...your car was created
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.49,0:36:05.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,又被史蒂夫·麦奎因代言\N{\fs90}by the swinging '60s and endorsed by Steve McQueen,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.69,0:36:08.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,他是有史以来最酷炫的人\N{\fs90}one of the coolest people who ever lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.36,0:36:10.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而就算这样\N{\fs90}and yet, somehow, you have managed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.46,0:36:12.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,你都能把沙滩车变无聊\N{\fs90}to make your beach buggy boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.27,0:36:13.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,-扯淡  -是有一点\N{\fs90}- Rubbish - It is a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.97,0:36:16.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,-它很没趣  -就像一场无聊的烟花秀\N{\fs90}- It is boring. - It's a boring firework display.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.14,0:36:19.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就是  -因为能正常运转才无聊\N{\fs90}- It is. - It's boring in that it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.41,0:36:20.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不 詹姆斯  -一点都不正常啊\N{\fs90}- No, James. - It doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.74,0:36:22.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,唯一出的一点岔子\N{\fs90}The only thing that has gone wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.44,0:36:24.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是油箱的轻微渗漏\N{\fs90}is a small leak in the petrol tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.58,0:36:26.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,其他一切都保持正常工作\N{\fs90}Everything else about it has constantly worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.65,0:36:28.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 每次我超你的车\N{\fs90}Do you know, every time I've overtaken you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.58,0:36:30.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,我看着你的车就想 "这太可怜了"\N{\fs90}I've looked and thought, "That's dismal."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.38,0:36:32.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,才不是 它有高贵而纯洁的血统\N{\fs90}It isn't. It has an elegance and a purity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.69,0:36:34.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,你总是说 "你不可能超我的车"\N{\fs90}And when you say, "You've never come past me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.89,0:36:38.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,我每50公里就超你一次 因为你没油了\N{\fs90}I come past you every 30 miles because you've run out of fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:42.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车前轮离地 油门卡住 电机脱落 螺丝失踪\N{\fs90}It wheelies, the throttle sticks, the alternator falls off, bolts fall out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.46,0:36:46.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那电机...  -你得给它配个翼片 然后外观就毁了\N{\fs90}- It... The alternator... - You've had to fit a wing on it, which ruins the looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.30,0:36:48.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是沙滩车的灵魂\N{\fs90}It's not in the spirit of the beach buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.10,0:36:51.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,而是某人迫切想要维护一个糟糕的点子\N{\fs90}but of a man desperately trying to justify a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.37,0:36:53.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这是个绝佳的点子  -根本行不通啊\N{\fs90}- It was a brilliant idea! - It doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.81,0:36:55.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在注意到了\N{\fs90}I'm fairly conscious right now
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.44,0:36:57.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的车在烧我车上的油\N{\fs90}your car is drinking the fuel out of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.58,0:36:59.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像一个塑料做的吸血鬼\N{\fs90}like a sort of plastic vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.51,0:37:01.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车很口渴\N{\fs90}Look, mine has been thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.05,0:37:03.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,-只是渴?  -对\N{\fs90}- Thirsty? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.55,0:37:05.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们继续争论\N{\fs90}JAMES: We continued arguing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.18,0:37:09.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,直到乔瓦尼提醒我们该睡了\N{\fs90}until Giovanni reminded us it was time to go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.12,0:37:10.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我并没有睡\N{\fs90}But I didn't go to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:15.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我有事要做\N{\fs90}because I had business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.76,0:37:17.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米觉得他很风光\N{\fs90}Right, Jeremy Clarkson thinks he's being flamboyant,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.80,0:37:20.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,但他不知道 我的空气动力学知识\N{\fs90}and he doesn't realize that my knowledge of aerodynamics
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.40,0:37:24.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,比他往别人车上的装假JJ的能力强多了\N{\fs90}will trump his ability to fit rubber penises to people's cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.02,0:37:42.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,我擦\N{\fs90}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.36,0:37:50.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 着火了\N{\fs90}Hammond! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.70,0:37:52.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,来人啊\N{\fs90}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.53,0:37:54.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 救火啊\N{\fs90}Hammond! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.71,0:38:02.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,第二天早上 当我们继续前行\N{\fs90}The next morning, as we resumed our journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.81,0:38:05.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,我感觉看开了一切\N{\fs90}I was feeling rather philosophical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.75,0:38:08.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,有一次我看见一位老太太摔倒\N{\fs90}I once saw an old lady fall over
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.91,0:38:11.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,她的购物袋滚到路对面\N{\fs90}and drop her shopping bag on the opposite side of the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.98,0:38:13.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,买的东西都掉出来了\N{\fs90}and her shopping fell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.69,0:38:15.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,其中有一个复活节彩蛋\N{\fs90}And amongst it was an Easter egg,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.39,0:38:18.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我猜是买给孙辈的\N{\fs90}which I assume she bought for a grandchild or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.86,0:38:21.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,彩蛋滚到了路中央 一辆车碾了过去\N{\fs90}and it rolled into the road and got run over by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.63,0:38:25.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最悲惨的事情...\N{\fs90}It was the most tragic thing I've ever seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.63,0:38:28.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,直到今早我看见了我的车头\N{\fs90}until I saw the front of my car this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.11,0:38:36.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,他毁掉的不仅仅是他自己的车头\N{\fs90}And it wasn't just the front of his own car he'd ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.21,0:38:45.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是不介意 但是詹姆斯的成果抖的实在太吓人了\N{\fs90}I wouldn't mind, but the rattling from James's workmanship is appalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.39,0:38:53.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管坎坷不断 但是我们快到了\N{\fs90}Despite everything, though, we were now almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.09,0:38:55.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,今天我们就要到达代表着\N{\fs90}Today, we would reach the beach that marked the finish
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.03,0:38:59.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,一段奇妙旅程的终点沙滩\N{\fs90}of what had been a spectacular journey
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.23,0:39:01.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,穿越一个奇妙的国家\N{\fs90}through a spectacular country.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.11,0:39:08.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,真应该被戳一下\N{\fs90}That deserves a stabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.21,0:39:12.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天呐\N{\fs90}RICHARD: Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.02,0:39:22.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,哎我去\N{\fs90}JEREMY: Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.25,0:39:24.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,乔瓦尼 你能准备下浴缸吗\N{\fs90}Giovanni, could you run the baths?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.20,0:39:32.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,来人啊\N{\fs90}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.57,0:39:35.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,这实在是令人惊叹的一块地方\N{\fs90}JEREMY: It really is an amazing part of the world, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.97,0:39:39.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,但美妙背后是残酷\N{\fs90}But everything that makes it amazing is harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.87,0:39:42.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,无情而且艰难的环境\N{\fs90}and unforgiving and difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.81,0:39:47.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,别抖了\N{\fs90}Oh, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.11,0:39:50.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,从来没人这么说过 但是纳米比亚...\N{\fs90}No one's ever said this before, but Namibia...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.02,0:39:54.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,真他妈是个美丽的国家\N{\fs90}...is a beautiful bastard of a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.86,0:40:05.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\fs90}And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.36,0:40:08.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们倒数旅程的最后几里路上\N{\fs90}as we counted down the last few miles of our journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.83,0:40:13.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的自制沙滩车都还在跑\N{\fs90}our home-made beach buggies were still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.51,0:40:17.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们青一块紫一块 但是它们向制片人证明了\N{\fs90}They were battered and bruised, but they'd proved our point to Mr Wilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.98,0:40:20.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们成功了\N{\fs90}They'd made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.41,0:40:24.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们还完成了其他事\N{\fs90}And they had done something else as well -
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.52,0:40:25.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们已经深入我心\N{\fs90}they'd got under our skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.02,0:40:28.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,比起一开始\N{\fs90}We liked them even more at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.22,0:40:30.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在我们更喜欢它们了\N{\fs90}than we had done at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.02,0:40:33.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得世界上每个人都应该开一辆沙滩车\N{\fs90}I think everybody in the world should drive a beach buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.73,0:40:37.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你会直面更多的事物\N{\fs90}because you're exposed to so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.36,0:40:38.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是天地水土\N{\fs90}Not just the elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.80,0:40:41.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有其他人的态度\N{\fs90}but the opinions of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.77,0:40:43.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你坐在普通的车里时\N{\fs90}I mean, when you're in a normal car,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.20,0:40:45.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,你挥拳头 摆手势\N{\fs90}you shake your fist and make gestures,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.67,0:40:46.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,你还大喊大叫\N{\fs90}and shout and yell,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:49.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你觉得被包裹 很有安全感\N{\fs90}because you feel cocooned and safe
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.81,0:40:52.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,对任何人都免疫\N{\fs90}and immune from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.01,0:40:56.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,但在沙滩车里 所有人就在面前\N{\fs90}But in a beach buggy, everyone's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.02,0:40:58.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太棒了\N{\fs90}It's brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.82,0:41:01.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一种友好的交通方式\N{\fs90}It's such a friendly way of moving about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.52,0:41:05.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,怀着这种信念 我们一骑绝尘\N{\fs90}And with that, we settled down
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.19,0:41:09.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,期待会有一条平坦的路通向海边\N{\fs90}for what we hoped would be a smooth cruise to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.53,0:41:11.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而并不是\N{\fs90}But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.57,0:41:14.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fs90}Oh, God! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.84,0:41:21.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太疯狂了\N{\fs90}This is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.38,0:41:24.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,哎哟我去\N{\fs90}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.61,0:41:29.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢不 它彻底坏了\N{\fs90}Oh, no! It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.28,0:41:33.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在这车的空气动力性能大受影响\N{\fs90}And now my aerodynamics are badly affected as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.39,0:41:37.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我勒个去\N{\fs90}Oh, my word!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.12,0:41:41.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米想就这样开到终点\N{\fs90}Jeremy is hoping to get to the finish line
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.26,0:41:44.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,坐在一堆你所痛恨的邻居\N{\fs90}in the sort of pile of scrap you hate your neighbors
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.33,0:41:46.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,会存在后院的那种破烂里\N{\fs90}for keeping at the bottom of their garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.04,0:41:51.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,要死要死\N{\fs90}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.91,0:41:58.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢不 油漏出来了\N{\fs90}JEREMY: Oh, no! There's petrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.58,0:42:01.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 别靠近他的车\N{\fs90}Oh! Hammond, don't go near his car!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.85,0:42:04.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,他车头全是汽油\N{\fs90}There's petrol all over the front of his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.25,0:42:05.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是嘛  -真的\N{\fs90}- Is there? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.99,0:42:09.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你着火了呢 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}What if it caught fire, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:16.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,只剩下最后48公里了\N{\fs90}With just 30 miles to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.26,0:42:20.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,强大的七缸V8真正开始玩大了\N{\fs90}the mighty seven-cylinder V8 really started to play up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.20,0:42:23.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不\N{\fs90}- Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.68,0:42:31.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后天色渐渐暗了下来\N{\fs90}And then it started to go dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.41,0:42:34.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,带来一堆麻问题最大的问题\N{\fs90}which presented us with the biggest problem of the lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.35,0:42:40.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,太差劲了吧\N{\fs90}That's just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.15,0:42:42.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦天哪\N{\fs90}Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.35,0:42:43.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fs90}Well, that's marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.06,0:42:45.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个快要把我亮瞎了\N{\fs90}That one is dazzling me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.03,0:42:48.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,而那个闪成转向灯\N{\fs90}and that one is showing me where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.80,0:42:52.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,这和想象中的差太远了\N{\fs90}This is far from ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.97,0:42:55.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,在夜幕笼罩之前\N{\fs90}Before pitch darkness fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.07,0:42:58.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们停下车来做些紧急修理\N{\fs90}we pulled over to do some emergency repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.77,0:43:00.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要用一些\N{\fs90}I'm gonna put some...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.54,0:43:03.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,某牌胶带来处理这个问题\N{\fs90}tape of a certain well-known brand on the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.65,0:43:07.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,用手拧紧就可以了\N{\fs90}Finger tight will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.18,0:43:10.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些修理太成功了\N{\fs90}These repairs were extremely successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.42,0:43:17.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 现在射到我脸上了\N{\fs90}Oh, it's swung into my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.22,0:43:20.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 我什么都看不见 比刚才还糟糕\N{\fs90}No, I can't see a thing. Agh! That's worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.70,0:43:25.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的亲娘 灯又歪另一边了\N{\fs90}Oh, God. Now they've turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.33,0:43:28.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 我的车又要斗鸡眼了\N{\fs90}Oh, no! My car's gone cross-eyed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.34,0:43:32.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个男的迎面驶来\N{\fs90}There's a man coming the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:34.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,他会怎么想我们\N{\fs90}What's he gonna think of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.67,0:43:35.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs90}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.94,0:43:37.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我他妈什么都看不见\N{\fs90}I can't see a bloody thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:42.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 哦这很好\N{\fs90}Thank you. Oh, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.25,0:43:44.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,大灯又被晃到正面去了\N{\fs90}It's shaken the headlight back round again!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.48,0:43:47.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶 又转回来了 就那么一瞬间好好的\N{\fs90}Yeah! No, it's back again. Oh, just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.69,0:43:54.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,这条起伏不平的路给前灯又带来了几个新问题\N{\fs90}Then the rough road brought some new headlight problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.39,0:43:57.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦什么都没了 没了\N{\fs90}Oh, nothing! Oh, no! Nothing! Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.33,0:44:01.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,我 我现在什么都没了\N{\fs90}I've got... I've now got nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.07,0:44:03.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 哈蒙德还有梅 你们能不能告诉我\N{\fs90}OK, Hammond and May, can you just let me know
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.30,0:44:05.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们现在的照明情况\N{\fs90}what your lighting situation is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.94,0:44:09.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,只要我抓着闪光灯控制杆 我就有光\N{\fs90}As long as I hold the flash lever back, I have light.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.88,0:44:13.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果我握着控制杆 一边是光 另一边闪光\N{\fs90}If I hold the lever, I get one light and one flashing light, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.91,0:44:17.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我要把手拿开去换档\N{\fs90}But I have to take my hand off to change gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.22,0:44:19.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后哈蒙德的车突然就变成了\N{\fs90}And then Hammond's car suddenly turned into
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.89,0:44:22.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,平克弗洛伊德演出用的灯光设备\N{\fs90}the lighting rig at a Pink Floyd gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.32,0:44:26.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么它一直在变 什么\N{\fs90}Why does it keep changing? What...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.56,0:44:27.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,乱套了\N{\fs90}And it's all got...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.30,0:44:36.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在只剩三公里了 三\N{\fs90}It's only three kilometres to go now. Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.87,0:44:42.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,他妈的啊\N{\fs90}Oh, fucking hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.84,0:44:45.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,没了 又亮了\N{\fs90}Gone. Coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.08,0:44:48.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,虽然我们看不到\N{\fs90}Although we couldn't see,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.85,0:44:51.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们知道肯定离沙滩很近了\N{\fs90}we knew we must be close to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.05,0:44:54.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是海边的沙滩\N{\fs90}It's not... you know, a seaside beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.22,0:44:57.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,肯定是在河流或者湖泊 或者别的什么\N{\fs90}It must be on a river or a lake, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.39,0:45:02.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,只是个上坡 我敢确定这不对劲\N{\fs90}This is uphill. I'm sure that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.76,0:45:07.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里真是个大下坡\N{\fs90}That's a big drop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.23,0:45:09.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可不想掉下去\N{\fs90}I don't want to go off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.94,0:45:12.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不确定这是否明智\N{\fs90}I'm not sure this is sensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.24,0:45:15.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,我读过的任何指南里都没有写\N{\fs90}Nowhere in any guide I've ever read does it say,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.98,0:45:19.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,在灯全坏的情况下 用沙滩车\N{\fs90}"Explore new territory in a beach buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.61,0:45:22.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,探索新的地域\N{\fs90}with your lights all broken."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.92,0:45:26.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,无法找到任何与沙滩有一点相近的地方\N{\fs90}Unable to find anything even remotely resembling a beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.95,0:45:28.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们停了下来\N{\fs90}we pulled over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.69,0:45:33.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们不能在黑暗里继续这么跌跌撞撞前进\N{\fs90}We cannot carry on just plunging around in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.93,0:45:35.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,希望能找到那个沙滩\N{\fs90}hoping to find the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.39,0:45:37.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且 先不说这个 那是什么声音\N{\fs90}And, anyway, what is that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.56,0:45:43.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,我会说… 是瀑布\N{\fs90}I would say that...is a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.64,0:45:45.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是不是你想在黑暗中碰上的\N{\fs90}Is it something you want to come across in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.01,0:45:49.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为关于那个声音我还想说\N{\fs90}Because the other thing I'd say about that sound -
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.07,0:45:52.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,可能我想多了 但感觉声音从脚下传来啊\N{\fs90}it might be my imagination, but that sounds as though it's coming from below,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.51,0:45:53.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,好像我们在瀑布之上\N{\fs90}like we're above it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.81,0:45:55.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们从那个小道上爬上来\N{\fs90}We have climbed up that track.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.28,0:45:57.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,而瀑布本身定义就是悬崖\N{\fs90}And a waterfall is a drop, by definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.58,0:45:59.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果我们… 我可不想在黑夜里\N{\fs90}If we're... I don't want to... in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.95,0:46:02.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,放弃 我不干了\N{\fs90}Abandon. I'm not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.45,0:46:04.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们明天等太阳\N{\fs90}We'll do it tomorrow. Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.59,0:46:07.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们仰望星空 再在纳米比亚过一夜\N{\fs90}Let's look at the stars and have one more night in Namibia.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.49,0:46:09.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们明天会找到的 而且风景美不胜收\N{\fs90}We'll find it tomorrow and it'll be fantastically glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.75,0:46:11.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,明天沙滩上见\N{\fs90}RICHARD: Tomorrow on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.55,0:46:13.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,乔瓦尼\N{\fs90}JEREMY: Giovanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.90,0:46:21.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,第二天早上 日光给我们揭晓了答案\N{\fs90}The next morning, daylight brought answers to our questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.48,0:46:25.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以它不是一条瀑布\N{\fs90}So it wasn't a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.28,0:46:27.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这是很多瀑布\N{\fs90}No, it was many waterfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.71,0:46:29.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,数以百计的瀑布\N{\fs90}Hundreds of waterfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.62,0:46:39.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都赞同的一点就是\N{\fs90}And they were just part of what we all agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.86,0:46:44.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我们见过最美的景色\N{\fs90}was the most beautiful view we'd ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.07,0:46:58.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 很多瀑布\N{\fs90}But...many waterfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.78,0:47:00.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我看不到沙滩\N{\fs90}No beach that I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.98,0:47:05.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,那个算沙滩吗\N{\fs90}Does that count as a beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.78,0:47:06.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是沙滩\N{\fs90}JEREMY: That is a beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.89,0:47:08.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我管那个叫沙滩\N{\fs90}I'd call that a beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.72,0:47:11.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-沙滩 -肯定是了 没有别的了\N{\fs90}- The beach. - That's got to be it. There's no others.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.79,0:47:14.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,各位 我们的探索终于有了结果\N{\fs90}Gentlemen, our quest is at an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.93,0:47:17.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们在这壮美中…\N{\fs90}Let us ride...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.80,0:47:21.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,驶去…\N{\fs90}in splendour... to...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.53,0:47:23.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-结束语说的不好是不是 怎么讲 -很动人\N{\fs90}- I'm not finishing that very well. What is it? - It's very moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.00,0:47:27.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想说点引人共鸣的 古雅的佳句\N{\fs90}I'm trying to think of something evocative and Victorian and brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.67,0:47:29.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,不如说“咱们开到那边完事了吧”\N{\fs90}How about “Let's go over there and finish our journey”?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.91,0:47:31.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 那是粗人之语\N{\fs90}No, that's Brummie rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.71,0:47:33.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,－它是 -是大实话\N{\fs90}- It is! - It's the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.75,0:47:37.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,无法找到合适的措辞来纪念这个时刻\N{\fs90}Unable to find the right words to mark the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.65,0:47:39.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们还是出发了\N{\fs90}...we set off anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.65,0:47:44.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶 就是这个\N{\fs90}Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.09,0:47:50.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们离我们的目标还有半公里\N{\fs90}We are half a kilometre from our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.63,0:47:55.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs90}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.00,0:47:58.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 死路 死路\N{\fs90}Oh, no. Path ends. Path ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.84,0:48:01.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,额\N{\fs90}Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.74,0:48:05.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊\N{\fs90}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.15,0:48:09.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果这条路不通\N{\fs90}Well, if this won't get over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.58,0:48:11.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,他俩的路也不可能通\N{\fs90}there's no way will theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.15,0:48:17.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们分头行动 寻找能够穿过石头的小路\N{\fs90}We split up to look for a path through the rocks...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.42,0:48:20.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不\N{\fs90}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.56,0:48:23.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是毫无希望\N{\fs90}...but it was hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.40,0:48:24.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\fs90}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.56,0:48:27.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 算了吧\N{\fs90}Hammond, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.40,0:48:29.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们开不过这个土丘的\N{\fs90}We aren't going down this hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.74,0:48:36.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是 就算我们可以越过这堆 更何况我们不能\N{\fs90}The problem is, even if we could get over this stuff, which we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.64,0:48:38.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 我们做不到\N{\fs90}RICHARD: No, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.28,0:48:40.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们看到我们和沙滩中间是什么吗\N{\fs90}...have you seen what's between us and the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.05,0:48:44.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,你看 绝对没办法可以开过或者开近\N{\fs90}Look at it. There's no way you could drive over that or anywhere near.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.02,0:48:47.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,-看 你甚至都不能到内陆 -不 我们过不去\N{\fs90}- Look, you can't even go inland. - No, we can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.59,0:48:49.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且你也不能绕过那个山\N{\fs90}And you can't go around that mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.35,0:48:51.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后从背面上来 因为都是悬崖\N{\fs90}and come at it from the back, cos they're cliffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.50,0:48:59.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs90}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.53,0:49:01.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs90}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.57,0:49:02.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,我有\N{\fs90}I've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.74,0:49:05.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,一个好主意\N{\fs90}...a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.20,0:49:08.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 -不\N{\fs90}- RICHARD: Oh, no. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.14,0:49:11.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们不能开到这里\N{\fs90}So we can't drive over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.24,0:49:16.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我们必须本人和车到达沙滩\N{\fs90}But we have to get us and our cars to that beach over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.08,0:49:21.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果能有某种\N{\fs90}If there were to be some kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.25,0:49:24.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,在那个悬崖上有个固定点\N{\fs90}A mounting point on that cliff, maybe, and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.49,0:49:25.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,干嘛\N{\fs90}Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.49,0:49:27.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 那边建个固定点\N{\fs90}No. Mounting point down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.63,0:49:29.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,那种距离？这可是很长的距离\N{\fs90}Over that distance? That's a huge distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.53,0:49:31.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,-差不多有一里 -不\N{\fs90}- It's about half a kilometre. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.13,0:49:32.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是你能想象它要承的力吗\N{\fs90}But can you imagine the forces on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.86,0:49:35.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,-固定物要很大才行 -很大\N{\fs90}- The things at the end are gonna have to be... - Huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.40,0:49:38.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,-巨大 -杰里米 我们并不都活在二次元里\N{\fs90}- Massive. - Jeremy, we don't all live in a cartoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.57,0:49:40.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们会死的 死翘翘\N{\fs90}We will die! Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.31,0:49:46.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,考虑到没有别的选择了\N{\fs90}Given that there were no alternatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.08,0:49:47.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们只好听从大猩猩的计划\N{\fs90}we had to go with the ape's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.05,0:49:53.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,也就是把我们的沙滩车变成缆车\N{\fs90}which was to turn our beach buggies into cable cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.52,0:49:56.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这个有两米多 -是的 足够好了\N{\fs90}- That's over two metres. - Yeah, that's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.96,0:50:00.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们前往附件一片废矿\N{\fs90}So we headed to a nearby abandoned mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.39,0:50:03.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,来寻找材料\N{\fs90}...to scavenge materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.10,0:50:07.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,这块能用吗\N{\fs90}JAMES: Is that bit any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.87,0:50:11.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们还有多少缆索 -四盘\N{\fs90}- How much more of that cable have we got? - Four drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.00,0:50:15.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你是提议把它改造成缠索盘吗 -是的\N{\fs90}- Are you proposing that that becomes a winding drum? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.41,0:50:17.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,重要的是\N{\fs90}It's very important...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.94,0:50:21.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要给哈蒙德的车加足重量\N{\fs90}we get as much weight as possible into Hammond's car...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.78,0:50:24.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了 好吧为了你们看乐呵\N{\fs90}for erm... well, for your amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.99,0:50:31.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,好 工具箱\N{\fs90}Right, toolbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.03,0:50:40.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你需要多少 -30米\N{\fs90}- JAMES: How much do you want? - JEREMY: 30 metres.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.91,0:50:49.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 那个圈你焊上了吗\N{\fs90}James, have you got that hoop welded in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.84,0:50:51.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有 接下来要搞\N{\fs90}No, that's my next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.15,0:50:57.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,几天之后\N{\fs90}Several days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.98,0:51:00.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,在没有任何\N{\fs90}and with absolutely no help whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.72,0:51:05.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,纳米比亚采矿工程师的帮助下\N{\fs90}from any Namibian mining engineers...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.12,0:51:09.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,世界上第一辆沙滩缆车已经准备好了\N{\fs90}...the world's first beach buggy cable car was ready, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.33,0:51:11.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,卧槽 停 所有人\N{\fs90}JEREMY: Shit! Stop, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.13,0:51:14.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,山羊在吃这棵我们用来固定的树\N{\fs90}The goats are eating the tree that we've anchored it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.13,0:51:16.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-嘘 山羊 -嘘\N{\fs90}- Shoo, goats! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.34,0:51:21.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们在吃树\N{\fs90}They were eating the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.64,0:51:23.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 正如我所说的\N{\fs90}Anyway, as I was saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.51,0:51:25.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,它长达一里\N{\fs90}it stretched for more than a third of a mile.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.01,0:51:28.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且几百米之下就是\N{\fs90}And since the drop to the crocodile-infested river
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.95,0:51:31.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,满是鳄鱼的河流\N{\fs90}was several hundred feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.18,0:51:33.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们决定让詹姆斯先来\N{\fs90}we decided James should go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.32,0:51:35.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们投票了 -真的吗\N{\fs90}- We had a vote. - Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.89,0:51:37.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 而且我们一致同意你第一个来\N{\fs90}We did, and we were unanimous you were going first.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.92,0:51:39.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 一下子变民主了是不是\N{\fs90}Right, so it's become a democracy all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.79,0:51:41.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 -没错\N{\fs90}- JEREMY: Yes, it has. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.73,0:51:43.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且不管怎么说 你的车是最轻的\N{\fs90}And anyway, your car's the lightest,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.36,0:51:44.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你烧掉了一半\N{\fs90}now you've burned half of it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.17,0:51:50.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在爬上来 天啊\N{\fs90}I'm climbing in. Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.20,0:51:53.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,当最高端的发电机发动时\N{\fs90}With the state-of-the-art generators fired up...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.38,0:52:00.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯为了这个旅行壮胆\N{\fs90}...James fortified himself for the journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.08,0:52:03.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,他这是喝酒吗\N{\fs90}Is he drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.02,0:52:07.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后就是开下发射台\N{\fs90}...and then simply drove off the launch pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.25,0:52:09.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,我滴妈啊\N{\fs90}JAMES: Oh, my God! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.89,0:52:13.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,卧槽 这太高了\N{\fs90}Oh, shit! It's really high!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.69,0:52:17.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太高了 我要把引擎关了\N{\fs90}It's really high! I'm turning the engine off.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.20,0:52:19.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们必须测试啊 -没错\N{\fs90}- We had to test it. -Well, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.33,0:52:22.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,-他必须第一个走 -不要看了以后觉得我们是坏人\N{\fs90}- He had to go first. - Don't look at us and think we're bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.47,0:52:25.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这是为了保证科学\N{\fs90}Because that was scientifically vigorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.34,0:52:32.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个缆车 这是个缆车\N{\fs90}It's a cable car. It's a cable car.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.98,0:52:35.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我坐过很多缆车 它们很安全\N{\fs90}I've been on lots of cable cars. They're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.71,0:52:38.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,-天哪快看他 这里是高的地方 -那太吓人了\N{\fs90}-  God. Look, he's... This is where it's high. - RICHARD: That's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.89,0:52:43.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这太高了 我不喜欢\N{\fs90}No! It's going really high! I don't like...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.79,0:52:49.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,我恨你们\N{\fs90}JAMES: I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.23,0:52:51.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好吧 -他不喜欢我们\N{\fs90}- OK. - He doesn't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.73,0:52:59.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管我很恐慌 沙滩缆车依然缓缓前进\N{\fs90}Despite my terror, the cable buggy kept on chugging through
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.14,0:53:03.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,越过了其实是安哥拉领空的地段\N{\fs90}what's technically Angolan airspace towards the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.98,0:53:05.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪 我快到了\N{\fs90}God, I'm nearly there!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.85,0:53:09.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,空挡 松手刹\N{\fs90}Neutral. Handbrake off.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.95,0:53:12.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,他就要做到了 他要做到了\N{\fs90}He's gonna do it. He's gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.32,0:53:13.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我到终点了\N{\fs90}I'm at the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.02,0:53:18.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,-他下去了 -安全降落\N{\fs90}- He's down. - That's a landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.92,0:53:20.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.93,0:53:22.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,-但是你知道吗 -什么\N{\fs90}- Do you know what, though? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.69,0:53:24.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我在这里做了点算数 -嗯\N{\fs90}- I'm doing maths here. - Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.56,0:53:27.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,很显然我们中有一个会死在这 对不对\N{\fs90}One of us is gonna be killed doing this, obviously, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.93,0:53:31.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我也这么觉得 对 -所以我们都在这里的时候 33%的几率\N{\fs90}- I'd say so, yeah. - So when we were all here, 33% chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.94,0:53:34.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在 我要以50%的几率做这个\N{\fs90}Now I'm doing it with a 50% chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.71,0:53:36.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你现在倒抢着做了 -我要下一个\N{\fs90}- Now you're doing it? - I'm going next.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.41,0:53:38.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我要下一个来 -你不可以\N{\fs90}- I can go next. - You can't go next.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.38,0:53:40.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么我不能下一个\N{\fs90}- Why can't I go next? -
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.91,0:53:44.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,让詹姆斯喝更多的酒来庆祝成功时\N{\fs90}Whilst James toasted his success with some more drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.88,0:53:49.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,我赢得了这场争论 准备发射\N{\fs90}...I won the argument and prepared for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.62,0:53:52.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么我的车是这个角度、\N{\fs90}Why is my car at this angle?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.89,0:53:56.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,也许是因为有个巨大的V8悬挂在后面\N{\fs90}Well, maybe because there's a massive V8 hanging out the back of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.33,0:53:58.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 好好好\N{\fs90}Right! Right, right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.86,0:54:00.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就… 出发吧\N{\fs90}I'll... here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.07,0:54:14.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的直肠刚刚像剧院幕布那样打开\N{\fs90}My rectum has just opened like a set of theatre curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.85,0:54:17.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是因为我怂 是因为我的沙滩车\N{\fs90}And for good reason, because my beach buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.68,0:54:22.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,比詹姆斯那烧焦了的残骸要重200公斤\N{\fs90}weighed 200 kilograms more than James's charred wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.42,0:54:28.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 他刮到草地了\N{\fs90}Ooh! Ooh! He brushed the grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.76,0:54:33.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,我很害怕 我说真的\N{\fs90}I'm terrified, I'll be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.57,0:54:36.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是从我出发到现在\N{\fs90}but, for the first time since I set off,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.37,0:54:38.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我第一次坐车里感到舒服\N{\fs90}I'm comfortable in my beach buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.05,0:54:53.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,接近沙滩 接近这场旅程的终点\N{\fs90}Approaching the beach. Approaching the end of the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.52,0:54:54.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我到了\N{\fs90}Here I come.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.92,0:54:58.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,着地\N{\fs90}And... touchdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.89,0:55:01.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.36,0:55:04.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,坏消息 哈蒙德 我做到了\N{\fs90}Bad news, Hammond. I've made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.16,0:55:05.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦好吧\N{\fs90}Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.76,0:55:09.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-先生 -太客气了 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}- Sir? - Oh, I say, James!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.37,0:55:11.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,事实上 酒还有剩的算走运了\N{\fs90}Actually, I was lucky there was some left,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.67,0:55:15.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为当詹姆斯一个人的时候 他觉得有点口渴\N{\fs90}because James had had a bit of a thirst on whilst he'd been alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.91,0:55:18.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,你好 下面的伙计们\N{\fs90}Hello, guys down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.28,0:55:20.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是站在巅峰的理查德\N{\fs90}It's Richard at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.61,0:55:22.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 我现在要做这个了 所以再见\N{\fs90}Right, I'm gonna do this now, so goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.49,0:55:29.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 我可不喜欢这个感觉\N{\fs90}Oh! I don't like that feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.76,0:55:37.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在到来的是 女士们先生们 理查德哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Here he comes, ladies and gentlemen, Richard Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.93,0:55:40.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs90}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.17,0:55:45.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以安心的是\N{\fs90}I could take solace from the fact that this system
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.07,0:55:48.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个系统已经测试过两次 成功两次 它是经过考验的\N{\fs90}has already run twice with their cars and not failed - it's been tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.94,0:55:50.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者我也可以更加现实一点\N{\fs90}Or I could take a more realistic view,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.01,0:55:55.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是那两个肥仔已经把它变得脆弱\N{\fs90}which is that those two fat oafs have already weakened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.78,0:55:58.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,再加上他后面有一堆破铜烂铁\N{\fs90}JEREMY: Plus he had all that scrap metal in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.08,0:56:00.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,这也是为什么所有的目光都注视着他\N{\fs90}which is why all eyes were on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.52,0:56:02.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 当我说“所有”目光的时候\N{\fs90}Well, when I say "all"...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.85,0:56:05.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,快看那边石头的颜色\N{\fs90}Look at the colours in those rocks over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.96,0:56:08.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,太美妙了\N{\fs90}It's... It's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.56,0:56:10.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,就在哈蒙德的左边\N{\fs90}Just to the left of where Hammond is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.67,0:56:16.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么我的车这么低 它很重\N{\fs90}Why's my car sitting so low? It is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.50,0:56:18.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是 为什么它更低\N{\fs90}It is... Why's it lower?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.34,0:56:21.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那色彩不可思议不是吗 -是的\N{\fs90}- The colouring is fabulous, isn't it? - Yeah, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.18,0:56:28.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管我很害怕 缆索依然坚固\N{\fs90}Despite all my fears, the cables were holding
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.75,0:56:32.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且拉着我越来越靠近另两位\N{\fs90}and drawing me ever closer to my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.35,0:56:34.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,要成功了 我看到沙滩了\N{\fs90}This is it. I can see the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.75,0:56:36.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,沙滩近在眼前 我们就要完成了\N{\fs90}I'm so nearly there. We are gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.46,0:56:39.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,来吧哈蒙德 快来\N{\fs90}Come on, Hammond. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.13,0:56:44.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就要做到了\N{\fs90}I'm gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.23,0:56:46.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,来吧哈蒙德 来吧\N{\fs90}Come on, Hammond. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.50,0:56:51.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs90}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.47,0:56:56.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,额\N{\fs90}Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.01,0:56:59.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么我停下来了\N{\fs90}Why have I stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.48,0:57:00.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 -来啊\N{\fs90}- Hammond! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.98,0:57:03.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我停住了 -哈蒙德\N{\fs90}- I've stopped! -Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.21,0:57:04.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,它就这么停住了\N{\fs90}It's just stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.92,0:57:06.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能做什么  它停住了\N{\fs90}What can I do? It's just stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.75,0:57:09.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里还有 大概 200米的距离\N{\fs90}There's, like, 200 metres to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.82,0:57:12.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,和我又没关系 又不是我说了算的\N{\fs90}I don't have anything to do with it! It's not up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.89,0:57:15.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,你俩什么都做不了吗\N{\fs90}Is there nothing you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.83,0:57:17.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,难过的是 詹姆斯醉的难以思考\N{\fs90}Sadly, James was too drunk to think,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.90,0:57:19.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我是个机械白痴\N{\fs90}and I'm mechanically inept.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.63,0:57:23.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,再加上 无论出什么问题 都是在那边顶端\N{\fs90}Plus, whatever had gone wrong had gone wrong at the top,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.57,0:57:25.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我们在底端\N{\fs90}and we were at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.50,0:57:26.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,动啊 动啊\N{\fs90}Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.04,0:57:29.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们真的什么都做不了\N{\fs90}There's literally nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.17,0:57:30.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们考虑了各方面\N{\fs90}We've assessed everything
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.61,0:57:32.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,你已经没救了\N{\fs90}and you're in a hopeless position.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.31,0:57:36.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可以再喝瓶啤酒\N{\fs90}We could have another beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.15,0:57:43.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我恐怕我们要下结论了\N{\fs90}We've gonna have to conclude, I'm afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.52,0:57:48.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,制片人是对的 沙滩车并不好\N{\fs90}that Mr Wilman was right that the beach buggy is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.23,0:57:51.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,伴随着这沮丧之情  是时候结束了\N{\fs90}And on that terrible disappointment, it's time to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.86,0:57:54.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们的观看 晚安\N{\fs90}Thank you so much for watching. Good night.
